title: 'Not Recommended | Not ultra thin
column5: These are ultra thin in the sense that they are not wide enough! Barely gives all area coverage. The only time I'd recommend using these is on those light flow days. These are NOT ultra thin as advertised and doesn't come in separate packaging either. It'd be difficult to carry it along. Pros: value for money if it suits your needs.
